channel.title: Talking Heads of Tiktok
channel.description: Curated Tiktoks and other videos of people speaking knowledgeably on a subject with brief vignettes.
channel.itunes:author: @lastchopperout on instagram

item.title: Episode 1 - October 13th, 2025 | TikTok Anthology
item.description:
Over an hour of short form presentations, ranging from 30 seconds to 10 minutes, curated and rounded up for a distraction free listening experience.
Most are added based off the hook alone since I use this for myself to listen to later. Which means I don't necessarily support or condone everything said in this anthology.
